reviewText: Run what ya brung.... Loved it.
Entertaining, but not very well produced. It's more a compilation of random events than a story.
Almost the same as ,The road to Bonneville. same guys, same talk same cars .a disappointment !
I love all of Brian Darwas' flims.  They truly show the hot rod culture.  This video highlights the Rolling Bones, one of the top Hot Rod shops in the nation. Watch the video and share the journey.
Awesome. Must watch for race fans.
